courses
Class Section

java.lang.Object
  courses.Section

public class Section
extends java.lang.Object

Sections represent actual course offerings. A Section has an instructor to teach it as well as a time when it is taught, whereas a Course does not. Sections are immutable. Certain fields can be null to indicate TBA--see constructor.

Invariants:

  • none

Version:
May 31, 2011: Jon eliminated TimeSlot fields., May 13, 2011, June 1, 2011: added java doc
Author:
Jonathan Caddey, David Liddington modified constructor, Greg Cloutier (added JavaDoc)
